{"tid":1512990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：只要在位一天，台灣絕對不會向強權屈服","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:59:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cca6ed905cfd91562a87353246922bd7229dcf09","tid":1512990,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"台灣總統蔡英文表示，隔着台灣海峽面對一個散播假消息挑撥分化的強權，<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣絕不會刻意挑釁中國，但亦不至於對中國的企圖天真無知</span>。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文今天透過錄影在「美國退伍軍團協會」(American Legion)年度全國大會發表談話，提到最新美國對台軍售案，強調採購軍備不是為了要引發衝突，而是實力才能讓霸權有所忌憚。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">她又重申，只要在位一天，台灣絕對不會向壓力屈服</span>，惟這個挑戰台灣無法獨自面對，需要全球理念相同國家的支持。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2232755/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2232755%2F&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=23618b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2232755/</a>"},{"pid":"d9f0d17f70dff8673fa44d0cbca7070a4a04d8a1","tid":1512990,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=30cbfdf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=59cba854